public abstract class ccell<FINALTYPE extends ccell<FINALTYPE>>
extends cell<FINALTYPE>

some legacy or simple games use just a "char" to indicate the contents of the cell. Most modern games use a "chip" subclass.

It's recommended to subclass chipCell or stackCell rather than this class.

Author:
ddyer
